'''哈立德·马哈苏德'''（{{lang-ur|خالد محسود}}<ref name=bbc2018/>；{{bd|1977年||2018年|2月8日|catIdx=S}}），又名'''哈立德·賽義德·沙伊納'''（{{lang|ur|خالد سید سجنا}}），是[[巴基斯坦|巴基斯坦]][[巴基斯坦塔利班运动|塔利班运动]]副首領及马哈苏德部族分支首領。在「巴塔」前首領[[哈基穆拉·马哈苏德|哈基穆拉·马哈苏德]]於2013年11月1日被[[美国空军|美国空军]][[无人飞机|无人飞机]]炸死後，沙伊納曾一度被視為接任「巴塔」首領的熱門人選。<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.ibtimes.co.uk/taliban-pakistan-khan-syed-mehsud-hakimullah-519058 | title=New Taliban Leader Named as Khan Syed Mehsud | publisher=ibtimes.co.uk | date=2014-07-01 | accessdate=2018-02-13 | archive-date=2018-06-16 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180616180417/https://www.ibtimes.co.uk/taliban-pakistan-khan-syed-mehsud-hakimullah-519058 | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/asia/pakistan/10422436/Khan-Said-tipped-as-new-leader-of-the-Taliban.html | title=Khan Said tipped as new leader of the Taliban | publisher=The Telegraph | date=2013-11-02 | accessdate=2018-02-13 | archive-date=2021-01-17 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210117092900/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/asia/pakistan/10422436/Khan-Said-tipped-as-new-leader-of-the-Taliban.html | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.foxnews.com/world/2013/11/02/pakistani-taliban-reportedly-replace-leader-killed-in-us-drone-strike.html | title=Pakistani Taliban reportedly replace leader killed in US drone strike | publisher=Fox News | date=2013-11-02 | accessdate=2018-02-13 | archive-date=2018-02-13 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180213080217/http://www.foxnews.com/world/2013/11/02/pakistani-taliban-reportedly-replace-leader-killed-in-us-drone-strike.html | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/asia/khan-said-named-as-new-pakistani-taliban-leader-after-hakimullah-mehsud-killed-in-us-drone-strike-8918433.html | title=Khan Said 'named as new Pakistani Taliban leader' after Hakimullah Mehsud killed in US drone strike | publisher=The Independent | date=2013-11-02 | accessdate=2013-11-02 | archive-date=2013-11-02 | archive-url=https://swap.stanford.edu/20131102160757/http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/asia/khan%2Dsaid%2Dnamed%2Das%2Dnew%2Dpakistani%2Dtaliban%2Dleader%2Dafter%2Dhakimullah%2Dmehsud%2Dkilled%2Din%2Dus%2Ddrone%2Dstrike%2D8918433.html | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://news.xinmin.cn/world/2013/11/03/22522194.html |title=巴塔首领 遭无人机袭击毙命 |date=2013-11-03 |publisher=新民网 |accessdate=2013-11-07 |archive-date=2014-05-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140529195512/http://news.xinmin.cn/world/2013/11/03/22522194.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

沙伊納曾與繼任「巴塔」首領的法兹卢拉不和。<ref name=bbc2018>{{Cite news |url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-43032261 |title=Pakistani Taliban deputy Khalid Mehsud 'killed in drone attack' |work=BBC News |date=2018-02-12 |accessdate=2018-02-12 |archive-date=2018-12-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181225102652/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-43032261 |dead-url=no }}</ref>2014年5月28日，沙伊納宣布退出巴基斯坦塔利班运动，称巴基斯坦塔利班运动“蜕变为一伙收费杀手”，其实施的杀人、抢劫、勒索以及绑架等行为不符合伊斯兰教教义。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.sina.com.cn/w/2014-05-29/063030253396.shtml |title=巴基斯坦塔利班两派分裂 |access-date=2014-05-29 |archive-date=2018-02-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180213022308/http://news.sina.com.cn/w/2014-05-29/063030253396.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>跟隨沙伊納脫離的一派自稱「巴基斯坦南瓦濟里斯坦塔利班運動」。<ref name=afpc01>{{Cite web |url=http://almanac.afpc.org/taliban |title=Taliban |website=almanac.afpc.org |date=2018-02-13 |access-date=2018-02-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180213195110/http://almanac.afpc.org/taliban |archive-date=2018-02-13 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

2014年10月21日，沙伊納被美國國務院列為{{Link-en|特定全球恐怖分子|Specially Designated Global Terrorist}}。<ref name=afpc01/>

2017年2月，「巴塔」宣佈沙伊納一派已重新加入。<ref>[http://www.longwarjournal.org/archives/2017/02/mehsud-faction-rejoins-the-movement-of-the-taliban-in-pakistan.php Mehsud faction rejoins the Movement of the Taliban in Pakistan] {{Wayback|url=http://www.longwarjournal.org/archives/2017/02/mehsud-faction-rejoins-the-movement-of-the-taliban-in-pakistan.php |date=20170205110627 }} - Long War Journal, 2017-02-04.</ref>

2018年2月8日，美軍無人機在[[北瓦济里斯坦|北瓦济里斯坦]]的戈维克地区殺死沙伊納。<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.voachinese.com/a/news-pakistan-us-military-strike-20180212/4249921.html |title=巴基斯坦塔利班证实美国无人机炸死其副总指挥 |publisher=美國之音 |date=2018-02-12 |accessdate=2018-02-12 |archive-date=2018-02-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180213022256/https://www.voachinese.com/a/news-pakistan-us-military-strike-20180212/4249921.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

